{"tid":673172,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)轟天猛將3 魔間傳奇 神秘電影","createTime":"2018-05-21T15:05:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T18:51:14.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ac3303c8bfa37590d52c492c597a280e09bc3ee6","tid":673172,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T15:05:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=QCkAzDZkjj3i0qnYFRiarU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=c13ee3ec\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=QCkAzDZkjj3i0qnYFRiarU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=5701ae75\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=QCkAzDZkjj3i0qnYFRiarU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=3a3ab5e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/f/f3/轟天猛將.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Ff%2Ff3%2F%E8%BD%9F%E5%A4%A9%E7%8C%9B%E5%B0%87.jpg&h=7b0fef84&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/yz4OSgZmMChsWlGe04mdBw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/nownews.com/4338ea1fdd8260dbf86681277e178f0f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fyz4OSgZmMChsWlGe04mdBw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fnownews.com%2F4338ea1fdd8260dbf86681277e178f0f&h=07f13d7d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/c/cc/Poster_of_I_Am_Legend.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fc%2Fcc%2FPoster_of_I_Am_Legend.jpg&h=6aaa8ec7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.浴血幫領導人巴尼&middot;羅斯（席維斯&middot;史特龍飾）帶領著手下李&middot;聖誕（傑森&middot;史塔森飾）、岡納&middot;詹森（杜夫&middot;朗格林飾）和托爾&middot;羅德（蘭迪&middot;寇楚飾）襲擊一輛前往軍事監獄的列車，幫助巴尼的老友死亡醫生（衛斯里&middot;史奈普飾）出來。死亡醫生被救出後，獨自一人解決列車上的士兵，並讓列車失控直衝監獄、造成監獄大爆炸。死亡醫生接受了巴尼的招募，回到了浴血幫。之後一行人到索馬利亞執行一件軍火商的彈藥走私任務，在那與海爾&middot;凱撒（泰瑞&middot;克魯斯飾）會合後展開行動。當中巴尼驚訝地發現，負責走私的軍火商就是浴血幫初期的聯合創始人康拉德&middot;史東班克斯（梅爾&middot;吉勃遜飾），原本走上歪路的他應早被巴尼解決，沒想到還活著。康拉德發現巴尼等人後隨即上了直升機，拿狙擊槍重傷凱撒並投下炸彈攻擊他們，之後便離去...<br />\n<br />\n2.2009年，「K氏病毒」（K Virus，簡稱KV）原本是研發出來用以治療癌症的基因改良病毒，在進行人體臨床試驗一段時間之後，開始產生類似狂犬病的意外副作用，並失控造成大規模傳染。除了造成世界上90%人口的死亡外，也使得約9%的人口變成狂暴、嗜血但體能驚人的變種夜行怪物<br />\n<br />\n3.<img src=\"https://www.telegraph.co.uk/content/dam/films/2017/01/04/deadpool_trans_NvBQzQNjv4BqZgEkZX3M936N5BQK4Va8RWtT0gK_6EfZT336f62EI5U.jpg?imwidth=450\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Ffilms%2F2017%2F01%2F04%2Fdeadpool_trans_NvBQzQNjv4BqZgEkZX3M936N5BQK4Va8RWtT0gK_6EfZT336f62EI5U.jpg%3Fimwidth%3D450&h=fe27bb56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n11 10PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 播完1先到神秘2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 薯片版<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=QCkAzDZkjj3i0qnYFRiarU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=24efaee0\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=QCkAzDZkjj3i0qnYFRiarU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=92d6d45d\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb0cb11e0ebba6d4752f2f9fb0754507d85e62a","tid":673172,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T15:31:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71e00cfdfca543628292efb6789a119f84a0bf42","tid":673172,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T15:59:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d21d2db910e07d5baaf7362344417eb71614be91","tid":673172,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T17:32:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"546903b8ff5e2cebc58e06edc0021751421e871e","tid":673172,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T18:28:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eda5270ef348abbec169ea6468ec9eb8645c7304","tid":673172,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":